# btbox SSH authorized keys
#
# Add the FreeBSD host's public SSH key here so btbox can execute
# bluetoothctl commands inside the guest VM over SSH.
#
# To obtain your host's public key:
#   cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub
#   cat ~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub
#
# Paste the full public key line below, then rebuild the guest image:
#   sh guest/build_alpine.sh
#
# Example:
#   ssh-ed25519 AAAA... user@hostname
